---
---

<footer class="px-6 py-16 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Join the community.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-lg mb-8">
        Comis is built in the open by people who believe AI should work for you - safely, reliably, and on your terms.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="https://docs.comis.ai" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-coral-btn hover:bg-coral-btn-hover text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Get Started
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/comisai/comis" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors border border-white/10">
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/comis" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors border border-white/10">
          Discord
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/comis_ai" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors border border-white/10">
          Twitter
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom -->
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <img src="/images/comis-logo.png" alt="Comis" class="h-8" />
        <span class="text-sm text-muted">Friendly by nature. Powerful by design.</span>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-muted">
        <a href="https://docs.comis.ai" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Docs</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/comisai/comis" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://discord.gg/comis" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Discord</a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/comis_ai" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Twitter</a>
      </div>

      <div class="text-sm text-muted">
        Apache-2.0 License
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Special thanks -->
    <p class="text-center text-xs text-muted mt-8">
      Special thanks to <a href="https://mariozechner.at/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="underline hover:text-muted transition-colors">Mario Zechner</a> for <a href="https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" class="underline hover:text-muted transition-colors">pi-mono</a>.
    </p>

    <!-- Acknowledgments -->
    <p class="text-center text-xs text-muted mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Comis exists because the open-source AI agent community proved that self-hosted assistants are not only viable - they're essential. Projects like OpenClaw showed what was possible and built a community around it. We learned from that work and chose to go deeper: agents with their own identity and soul, fleet orchestration with DAG pipelines, an 8-layer context engine that never loses the thread, and security-first infrastructure built for real-world trust. Different path, shared mission - AI that works for you, on your terms.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
